  "body": "Now that [PeerPool no longer restarts itself](https://github.com/ethereum/py-evm/pull/678), we need to make sure`p2p.Server` periodically check if it's still running, and possibly restart it if not. This is needed because p2p.Server runs the PeerPool in the background (with `asyncio.ensure_future()`)",
